skins.selfIntroduction: I am the Le Hardi-class destroyer, Le T¨¦m¨¦raire! I was never completed during that war, but I'm really happy that I can be with all of you now!
skins.acquisition: I've finally found you! Commander, it's a pleasure to meet you! Um, my name...? Ah! I'm Le T¨¦m¨¦raire, a Le Hardi-class destroyer from Iris Libre!
skins.login: Vas-y! Come on, the day's work is only beginning!
skins.details: Everyone here is so nice... but, there are some who seem hard to strike up a conversation with...
skins.secretaryIdle1: I made friends from several different camps yesterday! Ehehe~?

skins.shipDescription: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!
skins.acquisition: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!
skins.details: Commander, what do you think about my choice of swimsuit...? Ah, by the way, I also picked out Opini?tre's swimsuit!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Today's the day of the big beach volleyball meet! My friends and I are aiming for the top spot!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Opini?tre, are you busy practicing your "magic" again? Since we came all the way out here, you might as well have some fun...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Huh, a crab? ...Ehh?? It was just right there... Where'd it run off to?

skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Awawawa! Th-the strings are coming loose...!
